# IsoTpParallelQuery

This class is responsible for sending queries in parallel to multiple ECUs,
and returning a single result for each ECU.

## Motivation

The `IsoTpParallelQuery` class is useful when you want to send a query to
many ECUs and collect the responses.

## Usage

The `IsoTpParallelQuery` class is a context manager that accepts a list of
`CanData` objects. Each `CanData` object defines an address to send a query
to. It is up to you to determine the best way to construct these objects.
